data.description: Exuding charm, this 3 bedroom and 2 bathroom home in Stockbridge-Eagle Ridge greets you with hardwood floors on the main level and a bright, spacious living area adorned with vaulted ceilings, highlighting an airy atmosphere that invites relaxation. The focal point of the room is a cozy brick fireplace, adding warmth and character to the space. Adjacent to the living area is a light-filled dining room, offering picturesque outdoor views that enhance every mealtime experience open to the kitchen featuring a breakfast bar, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances.    The main bedroom is a true retreat, generously sized and boasting a spacious walk-in closet for all your storage needs. The ensuite main bathroom offers a luxurious experience with a separate soaking tub, dual vanities, and a glass-enclosed shower, creating a spa-like ambiance right at home. The secondary bedrooms are equally inviting, offering ample space and comfort for family members or guests. Step outside to discover the expansive, flat, fenced backyard and patio, offering plenty of space for outdoor activities and gatherings. A shed provides additional storage for tools and equipment, ensuring a clutter-free outdoor oasis for relaxation and entertainment.
